{"tid":829720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣細個同大個後嘅分別","createTime":"2018-09-20T16:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T02:25:02.000Z","uid":199869,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4be506e2687475a994bcd6a8f909af52c22b98bc","tid":829720,"uid":199869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:08:34.000Z","msg":"細個冇打飛機而家有打果啲就算啦 唔好講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先 細個好多野講 每次小學見家長 老師都話我多嘴 差啲因為同同學吹水 吹到記缺點小過 到中一二都係 但愈大就講得愈少 而家自覺口齒大不如前 講野口吃咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想做番以前想講咩就講咩嘅自己 但咁樣應該生存唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c3c8e8648178435c190054251cfcc434cfd510","tid":829720,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:51:04.000Z","msg":"細個過度活躍(外向) 大個咗過份安靜(內向)<br />\n不過由細到大同熟嘅朋友我都會搖身一變做痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25da1f4c299a6cc7970dd5e9d8e554a01e9b0290","tid":829720,"uid":115323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"細個好多朋友<br />\n大個得番幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c0ebf7a0768f12ddd0d8f8247e1374d1aa5c89","tid":829720,"uid":199869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25da1f4c299a6cc7970dd5e9d8e554a01e9b0290","tid":829720,"uid":115323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"細個好多朋友<br />\n大個得番幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccd38f857b4f576caf7a93adba29ffe3d16a4f2","tid":829720,"uid":199869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"48c3c8e8648178435c190054251cfcc434cfd510","tid":829720,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16: